CORPORATE EVENTS - PRIVATE ARENA AXE THROWING [6 - 150] GUESTS
Learn more
Looking for a rewarding, anti-boring, and fun Corporate event for your crew? Of course you are — that’s why you’re here.
Plan the Edgiest Corporate Event
Empower and build trust within your team by letting them chuck hatchets. We supply the axes, coaches, exercises, and experience. Good for up to 100 people.
Every event is managed by axe throwing coaches who will teach you to throw and run games and tournaments with your crew. — and here at Hatchet Hangout, we have the solution.
We Help Relieve Stress
Yea — we didn’t make this one up. Your fellow axe-throwers did. Our private events are un-officially rated the most stress-relieving group experience you’ll ever have.
MOTIVATE YOUR PEOPLE
Team building with axe throwing brings teams out of their comfort zone — and it’s a ton of fun! New experiences bring new perspectives, renewed spirits, and happier employees. Hint: happy workers = productive workers.
BUILD COMMUNICATION SKILLS
Let’s close Slack for a moment, put on our social hats, and do something face-to-face together. Axe throwing encourages new dialogue, exchanging ideas, and getting to know each other better!
BETTER ROI
Axe throwing offers great return on investment. Why spend $300 per person on a corporate retreat, when you can do something more fun and affordable right around the corner. Did we mention it’s a huge stress reliever?
RESERVE WHAT YOU NEED
Book a few lanes or rent the whole space. We can accommodate groups of up to 100 people depending on what you need. Plus, our venue is outside-food friendly. Turn our space into your place for any special events you have coming up.
Enjoy Axe Throwing with Coworkers.
Our corporate and team-building axe throwing activities are either 90 minutes or two hours in duration — enough time to have an amazingly fun time but not so long that your party gets bored. During this time, you have a dedicated axe throwing coach (or several coaches for larger groups) who walk you through the rules, how axe throwing works, and then begin with practicing and teaching you how to throw an axe.
Your group has dedicated axe throwing lanes where you can practice. Once you’ve learned the technique, we separate people into teams for fun games and host a team-based tournament to crown a winning team.
Food and drinks: You may use an outside caterer for all your food needs. We have a beer/wine/rtd mixed cocktail bar onsite as well as non-alcoholic drinks for sale.
We make your corporate event completely stress free. If you have any special requests or would like any more information, please don’t hesitate to contact us. The most popular times for corporate events are during the week, but if you’d like to book on a weekend, please let us know as soon as possible as times do fill up fast!
Event Structure:
We welcome your group and our AxeMasters give your party instruction on safety rules, technique, and practice throws. From there, we conduct fun axe throwing games to keep the event flowing. Throughout your event, you may break for food at any point (you supply any food or snacks you wish to serve).
Important Information:
Our AxeMasters work hard to make your experience one of a kind. Gratuities are never axe-pected but always appreciated. For groups of 10 or more, a 20% gratuity is required at the time of the event.

ABOUT HATCHET HANGOUT - AXE THROWING VENUE
Hatchet Hangout – Axe Throwing Venue is an indoor recreational range set up like a bowling alley with a bullseye target at the end of the lane.  Score points by throwing axes at a giant dartboard-like target. The closer you get to the bullseye, the more points earned.
We conduct casual and competitive axe throwing events for social, corporate, and league groups. All of our events are staffed with certified WATL instructors, helping groups nail the bullseye. No axe throwing experience? No problem! Experience Clearwater and St Pete’s premiere entertainment venue today!
HATCHET HANGOUT - AXE THROWING VENUE AND LOUNGE
Looking for something FUN to do? Need to destress and relAXE? Throwing axes with us is exactly what you need! No experience is required and we have coaches on site to teach you everything you need to know. We have taken every measure to make sure that this is extremely safe so the only thing you have to worry about is having a great time and beating your family for bragging rights!
Hatchet Hangout is a World-Class Axe Throwing Venue and Lounge Experience. Led by highly-trained “Axeperts” , guests participate in a variety of Axe throwing themed games. Hatchet Hangout is the perfect place for corporate events and team building exercises, as well as celebrations of all kinds including birthday parties, bachelor/bachelorette parties, divorce parties and even baby or wedding showers. Hatchet Hangout is extreme, social, fun!
Whether you are a local wanting a fun night out, a visitor on vacation, or someone looking for a great place to entertain your out-of-town guests, we guarantee you are going to have an AXEllent time! Check out our "What's New" page to see what fun events are coming up! Great fun for every occasion: Birthdays, Date Night/Anniversaries, Bachelor/Bachelorette Parties, Corporate Events, Team Building, Guys or Ladies Night Out, etc. Bear, wine & local cider are served.
